#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/20.install_on/arm_board.mdx:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "On an ARM board"
msgstr "На ARM-плате"

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/20.install_on/arm_board.mdx:18
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/20.install_on/raspberry_pi.mdx:17
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/20.install_on/regular_computer.mdx:17
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/20.install_on/remote_server.mdx:14
